I have created the project named Setting IP and added the four Liux Host and connected to the Ethernet switch through a LAN.
I have set the Ip address to the Host in a static way 10.1.20.1 and so on for all the host and I Have checked the Ip address in the command prompt using the Ip addr show command
This is the command that I have used to update the Ip address in command prompt.
auto eth0

iface eth0 inet static

address <ipaddress>

netmask <networkmask>

After updating the Ip
To check the Ip address is updated or not I have used the following commands to check 
ifdown eth0
ifup eth0
